PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-89 of January 11, 1995, which appointed MICHEL FOURNIER as a member of the St. Lawrence Seaway Authority by revoking the words "for a term ending July 10, 1997" and substituting the words "for a term ending August 9, 1997".
